    <date day="18" month="September" year="2025"></date>
    <abstract>
      <t>   This document outlines how an RPKI CA can migrate from one RFC 8181
   Publication Server to another.  The process is similar to the RPKI CA
   Key Rollover process defined in RFC 6489, except that in this case a
   new location is used for the new key.

	 </t>
